en_2024873_0	Three persons have been arrested in Embilitiya, Katugastota and Badulla, in three separate incidents, for the alleged possession of Cannabis.
en_2024873_1	It is alleged that the suspect arrested in  Embilitiya was in possession of  13 kilogrammes of Cannabis.  Another suspect, allegedly possessing Cannabis, was arrested in a raid carried out by the Anti-Corruption Unit of the Kandy Division.
en_2024873_2	Meanwhile, the Police Media Unit stated that a woman allegedly in possession of Heroin and a variety of Cannabis, more commonly known as KG, was arrested in the Udunuwara area in Badulla.
